Retro Phone Tools — third-party attribution
===========================================

JavaScript/web ports of public, reverse-engineered algorithms:

Unlock-code calculators (Huawei, ZTE, Alcatel, BlackBerry)
  Ported from: github.com/alexanderritola/Go-Unlock-Code-Calculator (MIT)

Nokia DCT4 firmware tools (decrypt, tone extraction, MThc→MIDI)
  Ported from: gitlab.com/Postrediori/mobile-phone-tools
    - dct4decrypt is based on decr.c / DCT4Crypt by g3gg0
      (github.com/g3gg0/DCT4Crypt)
    - ToneSniffer originates from wackypack/mtex (github.com/wackypack/mtex)
  No licence is stated upstream for mobile-phone-tools; these are independent
  reimplementations of the algorithms in JavaScript.

